Please do provide all the information asked for in the issue template (https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/new), for example which version of TensorFlow are you using?

Support for gradients of SVD was added in TensorFlow 1.5 (see #6503 (comment) and commit e1d9e4e). Is it possible that you're using an older version?
